OL,3,CNigel Farage 'betrayed' by ex-Reform
OL,4,Cleader in Wales who took pro-Russian
OL,5,Cbribes
OL,7,FReform UK leader Nigel Farage has said
OL,8,Fhe was "completely shocked" by bribery
OL,9,Fcharges brought against Nathan Gill,
OL,10,Fthe former leader of the party in
OL,11,FWales.
OL,13,FGill, 58, recently pleaded guilty to
OL,14,Feight counts of bribery, linked to
OL,15,Fstatements made in favour of Russia in
OL,16,Fthe European Parliament between
OL,17,FDecember 2018 and July 2019. His
OL,18,Factivities were said to include making
OL,19,Fpro-Russian statements about events in
OL,20,FUkraine in the European Parliament and
OL,21,Fin opinion pieces to news outlets.
