OL,7,FOn a visit to south Wales on Friday,
OL,8,F10 October, Farage responded to
OL,9,Fquestions about Gill's conduct and his
OL,10,Fconnection to the party.
OL,12,FHe said: "When we were in the European
OL,13,FParliament - I'm thinking 2019 - he
OL,14,Fand one of his colleagues said: 'we're
OL,15,Fgoing off to Ukraine, do you want to
OL,16,Fcome?' I said 'you must be mad'. I
OL,17,Fsaid 'I really don't think you should
OL,18,Fg o- it's a country beset by
OL,19,Fcorruption'. They defied my will.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
