OL,3,CNigel Farage 'betrayed' by ex-Reform
OL,4,Cleader in Wales who took pro-Russian
OL,5,Cbribes
OL,7,F"But not for a minute did I imagine
OL,8,Fthat he'd be engaging with a double
OL,9,Fagent there. Absolutely horrified. I
OL,10,Falmost find it hard to believe. I mean
OL,11,Fhere was a guy, a devout Christian,
OL,12,Fpreacher, a family man. I was really
OL,13,Fshocked when I heard it."
OL,15,FGill, of Anglesey, north Wales, was
OL,16,Ffirst elected as a UKIP MEP in 2014,
OL,17,Flater representing the Brexit Party
OL,18,Funtil the UK left the EU in 2020. He
OL,19,Fwas leader of Reform UK in Wales from
OL,20,FMarch to May 2021.
