OL,7,FWhen asked whether he had been a bad
OL,8,Fjudge of character, Farage said:
OL,9,F"Well, in this party he was briefly
OL,10,Fthe leader in Wales. And you know
OL,11,Fwhat, tell me a human being that
OL,12,Fhasn't at some point in their lives
OL,13,Fbeen surrounded by someone that
OL,14,Fbetrayed them and let them down."
OL,16,FFarage dismissed concerns about damage
OL,17,Fto Reform UK's reputation, stressing
OL,18,FGill had not been active in the party
OL,19,Ffor several years.
