OL,4,Cleader in Wales who took pro-Russian
OL,5,Cbribes
OL,7,F"It would be (damaging) if he was
OL,8,Fstill in the party," Farage said.
OL,9,F"Mercifully, he hasn't been for
OL,10,Fseveral years. It's awful, it's
OL,11,Fterrible, it's a classic clear-cut
OL,12,Fcase of corruption, and he's going to
OL,13,Fget his just deserts."
OL,15,FLooking ahead, Farage was optimistic
OL,16,Fabout the party's future in Wales,
OL,17,Fwith the Senedd election taking place
OL,18,Fin May 2026.
