OL,5,Cbribes
OL,7,F"Hundreds of people have applied to
OL,8,Fstand for us next year at the Senedd.
OL,9,FAmongst that number, somebody is going
OL,10,Fto emerge who will become the leader
OL,11,Fof the party in Wales. We're not there
OL,12,Fyet, we're still a work in progress,
OL,13,Fbut I'll tell you what, we're growing
OL,14,Fvery, very rapidly, we're getting more
OL,15,Fand more talent, and I think we'll
OL,16,Ffind someone good."
